author: niq
msg: Introduce ap_send_interim_response function and API, for interim
(HTTP 1xx) responses sent by an application or backend.

author: gkossakowski
msg: Moved management of ObjectModel to cocoon: protocol if it's used. This fixes various errors with disappearing values from OM when cocoon: protocol is used.
The side-effect of this hack is that values could be visible outside their scope in some rare cases. I haven't found any good way to avoid it due to complicated flow in SitemapSource.

author: gkossakowski
msg: Disabled PipelineComponentProxyDecorator because it is not used at this time anyway.

author: mrdon
msg: Replacing all usages of commons logging with xwork logging. Yay for closing memory leaks.
